{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, we used AraFacts Ali et al. (2021), a large dataset of Arabic rumors collected from five fact-checking websites.",
    "From those rumors, we selected only the ones that are expressed in tweets and for which the fact-checkers provided evidence in tweets as well.",
    "3 For false rumors, we selected a single tweet example of the rumor and all provided evidence tweets for it, which are then labeled as having disagree stances.",
    "Adopting this approach, we ended up with 118 debunking pairs.",
    "Additionally, we adopted a semi-automated approach to collect more debunking pairs using Twitter search."
  ]
}